file.name: schemaNoDuplicates.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Shop API
  version: '1'
paths:
  /v1/orders/{id}:
    get:
      summary: Get Order
      operationId: getOrder
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/OrderResponse'
  /v1/shippings:
    get:
      summary: Find Shipping information
      operationId: findShipping
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/FindShippingResponse'
components:
  responses:
    OrderResponse:
      description: Order information
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            type: object
            properties:
              data:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Order'
    FindShippingResponse:
      description: Shippings information
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            type: object
            properties:
              data:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Shippings'
  schemas:
    Order:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
        externalId:
          type: integer
        transactionId:
          type: integer
        userId:
          type: integer
        createdAt:
          type: string
          format: 'date-time'
      required:
        - id
    Shippings:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/Shipping'
    Shipping:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
        order:
          type: object
          properties:
            id:
              type: integer
          required:
            - id
      required:
        - id
        - order
